description:
Signal Vision is a next-generation sound data collection platform. It builds big data by collecting sound data through various IoT devices and DApps.

Signal Vision seeks to collect various sound data in various IoT home network, car black box, and so on as well as DApp in mobile by constructing and utilizing the token economy ecosystem of blockchain. In addition, our accumulated data construct Big Data Warehouse and provide new service, technical and academical discovery via statistics, analysis and machine learning using Big Data. As the number of collected data increases, API for statistics, analyzing results and sound data itself will be released so that anyone can develop new services and seek various businesses.
name: SignalVision
